narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned how to pick up new information quickly, but efficiently taking this course. This was my first online course, and I now feel very comfortable with the process.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I enjoyed talking to people during the class during breakout sessions. I also enjoyed the explorations because they were very helpful with going over the topics we learned. Sometimes, on weeks when we had a problem set and exam due, the workload was more intense, but still manageable.
